OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783941694
OL,3,CMore than 200 'troublemakers'
OL,4,Cdispersed as police tackle anti-social
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,FMore than 200 people have been served
OL,8,Fwith disperal notices in Thanet since
OL,9,Fthe start of the summer, as Kent
OL,10,FPolice looks to crack down on
OL,11,Fantisocial behaviour.
OL,13,FOfficers have been patrolling coastal
OL,14,Fareas in Broadstairs, Margate, and
OL,15,FRamsgate - and working to stop
OL,16,Funderage alcohol sales.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
