CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783941694
OL,3,CMore than 200 'troublemakers'
OL,4,Cdispersed as police tackle anti-social
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,F"We are proud of our coastal towns,
OL,8,Fwhich understandably draw large crowds
OL,9,Fduring the summer months and which are
OL,10,Fwonderful places to enjoy the warm,
OL,11,Fsunny weather", says District
OL,12,FCommander for Thanet, Chief Inspector
OL,13,FIan Swallow.
OL,15,FHe added: "We will use everything
OL,16,Fwithin our powers to ensure the small
OL,17,Fminority of people intent on causing
OL,18,Ftrouble here are held to account.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
