CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783941694
OL,3,CMore than 200 'troublemakers'
OL,4,Cdispersed as police tackle anti-social
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,F"Our enforcement action and work in
OL,8,Fthe local community is driving results
OL,9,Fand we will continue to keep measures
OL,10,Fin place to ensure those spending the
OL,11,Fsummer in Thanet can enjoy themselves
OL,12,Fsafely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
