OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783941694
OL,3,CMore than 200 'troublemakers'
OL,4,Cdispersed as police tackle anti-social
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,7,F"We appreciate the positive feedback
OL,8,Fwe have received from members of the
OL,9,Flocal community in regard to our
OL,10,Fincreased high visibility patrols, and
OL,11,Fwould like to assure residents,
OL,12,Fvisitors and local businesses of the
OL,13,Fextensive work that we continue to
OL,14,Fundertake to keep Thanet a great place
OL,15,Fto live, visit and work."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
